rnational Services UIC is an international community  Our student and scholarly pursuits touch all parts of the world  The Office of International Services  OIS  scholars  and academic departments  By giving to OIS  you are investing in UIC s global mission  Your gift will provide OIS with the financial support necessary to sustain critical university functions and explore innovative programming and advocacy for our dynamic international population  Additionally  gifts to the international student scholarship or emergency grant have the power to impact students on a personal level  often in times of great need  OIS is committed to comprehensive campus internationalization at UIC  we are excited to have your support   To make a gift  simply click on the button below Click here to make your gift  n  n Skip Nav UICOIS Navigation Menu Home About OIS Students Faculty  Staff  and Scholars Visitors Departments Programs Life in Illinois Alumni Resources Announcements OIS Events Calendar News          ois uic edu Facebook Instagram Twitter Web Privacy Statement Cookie Settings 